{
  "stem": "8359.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were, I guess, maybe trying to shoot it down, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I ran in back into the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened next?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Next, we were listening to the radios.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were told that Hitler attacked Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For the next couple of days, of course, we were very upset.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, actually, we knew it was coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because that August, the whole month of August, that was the whole topic, you know, that whatever was happening, Hitler-- this one trying to make a deal with him.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This one and that one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We knew that it's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Jewish men were drafted to the Polish, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were in the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because we were two girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember any of my uncles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think they were too old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the next couple of days, it was like, just sitting there listening to the radio and how they were attacking, and how they were almost in Warsaw, and you know, stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People started running, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] packing up their belongings, and going-- they figured that going deeper into Poland-- to Poland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we were so close to the--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How true it is, I don't know, but I understand that when the German army started marching into Poland, especially through the region where I lived, the sympathizers-- and Polish army was retreating-- the sympathizers were throwing down hot oil on them, on the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Volk-- that's right, the Volksdeutsche.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was just getting to it, because see, people started running.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody, whatever they could-- the wagon or something, a push cart, or whatever, they loaded up things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they ran to these villages and stuff.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
